          p.h3 B cells, plasma cells and antibody repertoires in the tumour microenvironment. Nat Rev Immunol.
            span.publications__more.publications__more--desktop(type="button")
          p.text Sharonov GV, Serebrovskaya EO, Yuzhakova DV, Britanova OV, Chudakov DM.
          .notes.publications__link <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41577-019-0257-x" class="notes--link" target="_blank">doi: 10.1038/s41577-019-0257-x.↗</a>
