            span.publications__more.publications__more--desktop(type="button")
          p.text Davey MS, Willcox CR, Hunter S, Kasatskaya SA, Remmerswaal EBM, Salim M, Mohammed F, Bemelman FJ, Chudakov DM, Oo YH, Willcox BE.
          .notes.publications__link 9(1):1760. <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-018-04076-0 class="notes--link" target="_blank">doi: 10.1038/s41467-018-04076-0.↗</a>
          .notes 2018 May 2

