          p.text Izraelson M, Nakonechnaya TO, Moltedo B, Egorov ES, Kasatskaya SA, Putintseva EV, Mamedov IZ, Staroverov DB, Shemiakina II, Zakharova MY, Davydov AN, Bolotin DA, Shugay M, Chudakov DM, Rudensky AY, Britanova OV.
